  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t在telegram某“山河大学”群、“白纸运动韩国”群，遭遇的若干网警，其态度、话术、套路，各种扣帽子、吓唬人、挑拨，以及两人甚至多人红脸白脸、捧哏逗哏、相互掩护（有点像以前中国各地都有的、长途汽车上“开瓶盖中奖”骗钱把戏中各骗子的表演），颇为典型，既阴险又有趣。在此发到这里供大家观瞻。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n（我不公开，国保也都知道且进入了这些群，所以我公开只有利于暴露其嘴脸，而没有对无辜者的额外伤害）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZWE3M2Q1ZGIyNjcyYzQ3MWY3NWIwLnBuZz93aWR0aD03NTAmaGVpZ2h0PTEyMTc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ea73d5db2672c471f75b0.png?width=750&amp;height=1217\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ea73d5db2672c471f75b0.png?width=750&amp;height=1217\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ea73d5db2672c471f75b0.png?width=750&amp;height=1217\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMmQyNTMwYmZiZTA0NzE4MzAxMDMwLnBuZz93aWR0aD03NTAmaGVpZ2h0PTEyMTA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2d2530bfbe04718301030.png?width=750&amp;height=1210\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2d2530bfbe04718301030.png?width=750&amp;height=1210\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2d2530bfbe04718301030.png?width=750&amp;height=1210\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOTAyZjI4MGYzOTgyZTllZmE5YmU4LnBuZz93aWR0aD03NTAmaGVpZ2h0PTExNjg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/902f280f3982e9efa9be8.png?width=750&amp;height=1168\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/902f280f3982e9efa9be8.png?width=750&amp;height=1168\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/902f280f3982e9efa9be8.png?width=750&amp;height=1168\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYTVjMWQzMWI5NzAxN2M5Yjg0MTk4LnBuZz93aWR0aD03NTAmaGVpZ2h0PTExNzY\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://t